Name: lichao

Specification:
	Simulation of a 3D spherical ball bouncing in a box, Aim to learn the basic notions of physical simulation and to get the use of OPENGL and GLUT.

Operations:
	1."make" the file, run it(./bounceInBox) 		
	2.Press "t" or "T" to throw the ball. To speed up, do not let button up
	3.Press left button of mouse to rotate and roll the middle button to change the viewpoint
	4.Press "f" or "F" to set the center of focus 
	5.Press "m" or "M" to change the color of box
	4.Press "r" or "R" to reset. then go to step 2
	5.Press "q" or "Q" to quit
